{"tid":1719382,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"著風縷 唔好黑衫一個人走","createTime":"2019-11-14T05:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T08:19:28.000Z","uid":34047,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"33b5304f809a85230b05fe7a836dabc8156224b6","tid":1719382,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"講緊打機<br />\n個角色set野時著黑風縷<br />\n走時留意有冇比人釘上跟住<br />\n唔好一個人走 適時除黑風縷<br />\n女仔特別要小心<br />\n確保冇人跟先好一個人<br />\n否則繼續團隊行動直到甩開跟縱者<br />\n<br />\n另外，打機果時勇者對付施襲者自衛時：<br />\n1. 人少就閃 人多做野時就一定要包好自己<br />\n2. 取手腳(最快係R斷手？) 落手快閃得快<br />\n3. 小心比人跟 會有花生藍絲/狗報串"},{"pid":"c5a98afccd01b8e7fa8ca0e73c4cecfba82adaa4","tid":1719382,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:48:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49a01ffb11c1230ece564172d7e35a60186d712e","tid":1719382,"uid":11396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"換衫換衫換衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9f90c026f4951504a36b28a31f4ed7ce4e0924","tid":1719382,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"推"}]}